RuneScape 3 Hiscores Lookup as a chrome extension.

This extension is still in active development.

A few things I'd like to include are:
* OSRS Hiscores (Potentially as a separate extension)
* Support for virtual levels
* Golden trim around 99 stats, identifiers for 120 stats and 200m xp stats
* A loading animation
* Error/warning notifications
* Mouse-over to view xp

Feel free to send any suggestions.

Resources are the property of Jagex. This extension generates no revenue.
